  "publications_raw": [
    "Books\nAmrita Ganguly and Bijan Paul, “Tiny Blind Assistive Humanoid Robot”, published with IntechOpen’s Online First service, Indexed by Web of Science - Book Citation Index, Microsoft Academic, Google Scholar, Crossref, OAPEN, OpenAIRE, 2021. Link:\nhttps://www.intechopen.com/online-first/tiny-blind-assistive-humanoid-robot",
    "Journal Articles\nMd. Asifuzzaman Jishan, Khan Raqib Mahmud, Abul Kalam Al Azad, Mohammad Rifat Ahmmad Rashid,\nBijan Paul\n, Md. Shahabub Alam, “Bangla language textual image description by hybrid neural network model”, Indonesian Journal of Electrical Engineering and Computer Science, September 2020, ISSN: 2502-4752\nBijan Paul\n, Md. Ibrahim and Md. Abu Naser Bikas,”\nVANET Routing Protocols: Pros and Cons\n”. In International Journal of Computer Applications (IJCA), Volume 20– No.3, April 2011.\nBijan Paul\n, Md. Ibrahim and Md. Abu Naser Bikas, “\nExperimental Analysis of AODV & DSR over TCP & CBR Connections with Varying Speed and Node Density in VANET\n”. In International Journal of Computer Applications (IJCA), Volume 24– No.4, June 2011.\nBijan Paul\n, Md. Ibrahim and Md. Abu Naser Bikas, “\nPerformance Evaluation of AODV & DSR with Varying Pause Time & Node Density over TCP&CBR Connections in VANET\n”. In International Journal of Computer Science and Network Security (IJCSNS), Volume 11– No.7, July 2011. Link:\nBijan Paul\n, Md. Ibrahim and Md. Abu Naser Bikas, “\nPerformance Evaluation of AODV & DSR with Varying Pause Time & Speed Time Over TCP & CBR Connections in VANET\n”. In International Journal of Computer Science Issues (IJCSI), Volume 9, Issue 1, January 2012 issue. Link:\nBijan Paul\nand Mohammed J. Islam, “\nSurvey over VANET Routing Protocols for Vehicle to Vehicle Communication\n”. In IOSR Journal of Computer Engineering (IOSR-JCE), Volume 7, Issue 5, PP 01-09, Nov-Dec. 2012.",
    "Conference Proceedings\nMd. Ruhul Amin,\nBijan Paul\nand Faisal Ahamed Khan, “\nBi-Lingual Screen Reading Software for the People with Visual Impairments\n”. In 15th International Conference on Computer and Information Technology by ICCIT 2012, co-sponsored by\nIEEE\n.\nBijan Paul\n, Aditi Roy, Sanjit Kumar Paul, “\nComparison of DSR, AODV, and DSDV Routing Protocols with Varying Pause Time & Node Density over TCP & CBR Connections in VANET\n”, 2014 Sixth IEEE International Conference on Computational Intelligence and Communication Networks, 14-16th November 2014,\nIEEE\nPublisher.\nBijan Paul\n, Kaysar Ahmed Bhuiyan, Kaniz Fatema, Partha Pratim Das, “\nAnalysis of AOMDV, AODV, DSR, and DSDV Routing Protocols for Wireless Sensor Network\n”, 2014 Sixth IEEE International Conference on Computational Intelligence and Communication Networks, 14-16th November 2014.\nIEEE\nPublisher.\nFaisal Ahmed Khan,\nBijan Paul\n, “\nScreen reading with Bangla & English audio assistance bi-lingual supported software ‘Mongol Dip’ for visually impaired people\n”, 17th International Conference on Computer and Information Technology, 2014, 22-23rd December 2014.\nIEEE\nPublisher.\nAditi Roy,\nBijan Paul\n, Sanjit Kumar Paul, “\nVANET Topology Based Routing Protocols & Performance of AODV, DSR Routing Protocols in Random Waypoint Scenarios\n”, International Conference on Computer and Information Engineering ICCIE 2015 26-27 November 2015.\nIEEE\nPublisher.\nAtikur Rahman, Mrinal Kar,\nBijan Paul\n, “\nAn experiment for isolating normal & malicious node behavior in VANET\n”, 2017 IEEE Region 10 Humanitarian Technology Conference (R10-HTC), 21-23 Dec. 2017.\nIEEE\nPublisher.\nMd. Mohiuddin Ahmed, Suraiya Banu,\nBijan Paul\n,\n“Real-time air quality monitoring system for Bangladesh's perspective based on Internet of Things\n”, 3rd International Conference on Electrical Information and Communication Technology (EICT), 7-9 Dec. 2017.\nIEEE\nPublisher.\nAmrita Ganguly and Jasmine Ara and\nBijan Paul\n,\n“Design and Development of Tiny Humanoid Walking and Dancing Robot with Obstacle Detection for Visual Impaired People”,\nSmart Trends in Computing and Communications: Proceedings of SmartCom 2020,\nSpringer\nPublisher.\nShanta Saha, Md. Omar Sharif Rajme,\nBijan Paul\n, Mohammad Rifat Ahmmad Rashid and Khan Raqib Mahmud, “Life Saver Robotic Car for Accidental or Disaster Place Emergency Situation”, ICT4SD – 2020 5th International Conference, Indexed by ISI Proceedings, EI-Compendex, DBLP, SCOPUS, Google Scholar and\nSpringerlink\n.\nMoumita Kabir, Fatima Noor Popy,\nBijan Paul\n, Mohammad Rifat Ahmmad Rashid and Khan Raqib Mahmud, “Obstacle avoiding and Fire Extinguishing Robot for Everyday Fire Security”, ICT4SD – 2020 5th International Conference, Indexed by ISI Proceedings, EI-Compendex, DBLP, SCOPUS, Google Scholar and\nSpringerlink\n.\nFatema Zaman Sinthia, Afsana Nasir,\nBijan Paul\n, Mohammad Rifat Ahmmad Rashid and Md Nasim Adnan, “Implementation of OSPFv3 in IPv4 and IPv6 for Established a Wide Area Network”, ICT4SD – 2020 5th International Conference, Indexed by ISI Proceedings, EI-Compendex, DBLP, SCOPUS, Google Scholar and\nSpringerlink\n."
